name: Sky Farm Dive
description: You had enough of working in the farms by the countryside and want to change your career and lifestyle. Now, you embark on a journey to become the world's greatest businessperson! But the deeply attached farm animals that you raised don't want you to go. They will do whatever it takes to stop you even in your dreams! Avoid your farm animals as you glide across the sky and earn enough money along the way to reach your dream job!
